Awesomely cool, I'll email you and another Tucson AL member offlist when we
figure out when we are going. It will probably be in a week or so.

Thanks Sybelle!
Jacki

-----Original Message-----
From: AlwaysLearning@yahoogroups.com
[mailto:AlwaysLearning@yahoogroups.com]On Behalf Of Arnold and Sybelle
Sent: Monday, June 20, 2005 9:51 AM
To: AlwaysLearning@yahoogroups.com
Subject: [AlwaysLearning] Re:Travel ,AZ, Katchner Caverns


Hey!! We live in Benson,AZ, and are friends with Heather. you all come visit
us when you go to the caves, which are only 10 minutes from our house. How
fun that would be!
We don't have a "real" pool, but one of those 15 ft. round ones that is 4
ft. deep. It is good for cooling off, though. And our house is cool too....

I'd like to extend a welcome to anyone travelling our way. There's plenty of
room on our 5 acres for an RV. And electric and water too. Or, stay in our
RV. We travelled around in that for 5 months, with the 4 of us. It would
sleep 5 for a short while too.

Sybelle
(Ingo,11 and Bibi,almost 8)
